Package: catchment
Type: Package
Title: Calculate spatial access and availability metrics
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2021-11-25
Authors@R: c(
    person("Biocomplexity Institute", role = c("aut", "cph")),
    person("Micah", "Iserman", role = "cre", email = "micah.iserman@gmail.com")
  )
Description: Offers a range of spatial access and availability metrics, including
  variants of 2- and 3-step floating catchment areas: 2SFCA (Luo & Wang, 2003) <doi:10.1068/b29120>,
  E2SFCA (Lou & Qi, 2009) <doi:10.1016/j.healthplace.2009.06.002>, KD2SFCA / G2SFCA (Dai, 2010)
  <doi: 10.1016/j.healthplace.2010.06.012>, and 3SFCA (Wan, Zou, & Sternberg, 2012)
  <doi:10.1080/13658816.2011.624987>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: cli, methods, Matrix, lingmatch, sf, jsonlite
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    splot,
    leaflet,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.2.2
Roxygen: list(old_usage = TRUE)
